# Scraper Console

Standalone dev app for web scraping experiments. **Isolated from arcane-reader** (no shared UI, no project import).

## Module map

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `apps/scraper-console/src/` | Express server, `/api/scraper/*`, run buffer |
| `apps/scraper-console/ui/` | Preact SPA at `/scraper/` |
| `apps/scraper-console/shared/` | Browser-safe types |
| `packages/scraper/` | `@arcane/scraper` library (adapters, `onStage`) |

## URLs (dev)

- UI: `http://localhost:PORT/scraper/`
- API: `http://localhost:PORT/api/scraper/*`
- Default `PORT=3000`; use `3002` when reader occupies 3000

## Commands

```bash
# from monorepo root
npm run dev:scraper
npm run test:scraper
npm run build:scraper
```

## Conventions

- Do not import from `arcane-reader/src/**`
- UI primitives live in `ui/components/ui/` (copied from debug-app pattern, not shared)
- Sync scrape only; no BullMQ, Supabase, or Redis
